---

{% from "components/hint/macro.njk" import hint %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>Hint text is rendered with an <code>id</code> so the associated
  form field can reference it via <code>aria-describedby</code>.</p>

<div>
  <label for="nhs-number">NHS number</label>
  {{ hint({
    id: "nhs-number-hint",
    text: "It is a 10-digit number, for example 485 777 3456."
  }) }}
  <input id="nhs-number"
         type="text"
         aria-describedby="nhs-number-hint"
         inputmode="numeric"
         autocomplete="off">
</div>

<h2>With HTML content</h2>
<div>
  <label for="date-of-birth">Date of birth</label>
  {{ hint({
    id: "dob-hint",
    html: "For example, <strong>27 3 1970</strong>."
  }) }}
  <input id="date-of-birth"
         type="text"
         aria-describedby="dob-hint">
</div>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>Always link the hint to its field with <code>aria-describedby</code>
  so screen readers announce the guidance alongside the field label.</p>
